data.description: This home is truly a dream come true! Enjoy over 3,500 Square feet of living space - plenty of room for the whole family to spread out. Four generously-sized bedrooms, three full baths, and an updated kitchen with tile flooring, ample counter and storage space, and a center island allow for comfortable living and convenience. Step outside for a little fresh air and take in the idyllic view of the mature trees surrounding the property. There's even plenty of outdoor space for entertaining and play. Your search ends here - don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your own!
